news.title: Lucknow development body to develop Udyog Nagar, Naimish Nagar
news.para: Singh said that Udyog Nagar will be developed over 5,610 acres in Sadar and Sarojininagar tehsils. Land was identified in villages, including Bhaliya, Adampur Indwara, Behru, Jaliamau, Madarpur and Ibrahimganj.

news.title: Centre set to push amendments to DDA, to give fillip to land pooling policy
news.para: The Centre is planning to push amendments to the Delhi Development Act which will make land pooling mandatory for all residents if a certain percentage -- 70% -- of owners of land in an area agree to pool land.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh to launch three-month drive to regularise or raze unauthorised constructions
news.para: During a review of the housing development authorities, it was found that out of the 2.50 lakh complaints pertaining to unauthorised and illegal construction activity forwarded to authorities during the 2024-25 financial year, only 3,507 have been disposed of, while the remaining ones remain pending.
